The evidence with the title '2016 elections: i'm getting rich off your vote - POLITICO Magazine ' says Dec 11, 2015  ... Of the many superlatives history will bestow on America 's 2016 presidential race, here 's one you might not have heard: it will be the biggest political gambling  ... Axe to grind , i have one simple agenda : to make as much money as humanly possible , right up until november 8, 2016, betting on your elections. 
